snippet.title: Amelia's Garden | Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Repair these pots and start a brand new rooftop garden!
Turn this empty rooftop into your own green corner in the city. Glue together colorful pots, plant various seeds, and share your harvest with friends in Amelia’s Garden!

Wishlist no on the Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/amelias-garden-switch/

Don't forget to follow us on 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RedDeer_Games
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RedDeerGames
and Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reddeer_games/
